            <h2>Examples</h2>

            <p>To install something (in our case <a href="https://github.com/chaliy/psurl/">PsUrl</a>) from central directory just type:</p>

            <pre><code>install-module PsUrl</code></pre>

            <p>Of course, you can browse/search modules directory:</p>

            <pre><code>Get-PsGetModuleInfo Posh*</code></pre>
